No. 09-864 (R46-010). KBR Technical Services Inc., et al., Petitioners v. Jamie Leigh Jones. 559 U.S. 998, 130 S. Ct. 1756,

176 L. Ed. 2d 224,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 2340. March 11, 2010.

The petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Fifth Circuit in the above-entitled case was dismissed today pursuant to this Court’s Rule 46.1.

Same case below, 583 F.3d 228.
